title: Presto® Foldaway® Cool Touch Electric Griddle
description:
Special Foldaway™ feature allows legs to fold up for compact storage, saving valuable cabinet space.

Efficient "square" shape holds more pancakes, eggs, and sandwiches than most conventional rectangular griddles.

Cool-touch base surrounds the grilling surface on the front and both sides. Control Master® heat control maintains the proper cooking temperature automatically. Premium nonstick surface and slide-out drip tray for easy cleaning. Fully immersible and dishwasher safe with the heat control removed. Fits in most dishwashers and standard 18-inch kitchen cabinets.

transcripts: The presto cool touch electric foldaway griddle is great for every meal, breakfast, lunch, and dinner a cool touch base surrounds the cooking surface on the front and both sides and the 14 by 15-inch grilling surface is nearly square for efficient shape that holds more eggs, pancakes, and sandwiches than conventional rectangular griddles. It features a control master heat control that maintains the proper cooking temperature automatically. A premium non-stick surface providing stick free cooking and a built-in backstop ledge for easy food handling the Presto foldaway griddle is ideal for making family size batches of pancakes, eggs, hash browns, sausages, bacon and more. When you're done the slide-out drip tray removes for quick clean-ups plus the grill is fully immerse-able with the heat control detached and fits in most dishwashers and it's simple to store. The exclusive foldaway feature allows the legs to fold up for compact storage saving valuable cabinet space it fits in most standard 18 inch cabinets right next to your cookie sheets and cutting boards the Presto cool touch electric foldaway griddle for delicious meals, easy cleanup, and compact storage. Get one today.
